_sText:
Well, here it is, after around 2 months of development from the origional idea, I bring you cs_office2.

My main objective was to create a sequal to the map cs_office, trying to stay with the origional style as closley as possible and creating a whole new map that plays completlyy differently.

This map has 40 player spawn points, has the radar overview images and has HDR lighting to finish it off.  Decent frames throughout the whole map, even when running bots.

Finally, I hope you all enjoy playing it!
